{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"真的，你们喜爱现世的生活，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"而不顾后世的生活。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"在那日，许多面目是光华的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"是仰视着他们的主的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"在那日，许多面目是愁苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们确信自己必遭大难。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"真的，灵魂达到锁骨，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"有人说：谁是祝由的？”"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他确信那是离别。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"（死时）胫与胫相缠结。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"在那日，他只被驱赶到你的主那里。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"他没有信道，也没有礼拜。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"他否认真理，背弃正道，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"然后傲慢地走回家去。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"毁灭渐渐地临近你，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"毁灭已渐渐地临近你。”"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"难道人猜想自己是被放任的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"难道他不曾是被射出精液吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"然后，他变成血块，而安拉加以创造他，使之成为肢体完全的人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"他用精液造化两性，男的和女的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"难道那样的造化者不能使死人复活吗？"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"人确实经历一个时期，不是一件可以记念的事物。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我确已用混合的精液创造人，并加以试验，将他创造成聪明的。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"我确已指引他正道，他或是感谢，或是辜负。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我确已为不信者预备许多铁链、铁圈和火狱。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"善人们必得饮含有樟脑的醴泉，"}]}